             was indicted for <rs id="t17980523-19-off97" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17980523-19-off97" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17980523-19-off97" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17980523-19-cd98" type="crimeDate">14th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980523-19-off97 t17980523-19-cd98"></join>, a printed book bound in leather, value 1s. four pounds of pork, value 2s. and a wooden box, value 6d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17980523-19-victim201" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Whitmarsh
